IRSSI
ds terminal:
irssi
/connect chat.freenode.net // connect to server irc
/nick  <NICKNAME> //enter a nickname for chatting
/join #CHANNEL-NAME // create a unique channel //ex #CHNL1

//opening irssi in another device:
irssi
/connect chat.freenode.net
/nick  <NICKNAME>
/join #CHANNEL-NAME //ex #CHNL1
//Now chat!
/cs register #CHANNEL-NAME  <password> //ex CHNL1 password
/topic <TOPIC-NAME> //ex  secretchannel
/invite <NAME-USER>  #CHANNEL-NAME // invit unser to join channel
/join #CHANNEL-NAME <PASSWORD> // user2 join #CHNL1 password

/EXIT // exit irssi


